    "description": "现在预购即可享有九折！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/af0584148a6f56d1ce31b8b4d47dc5dd.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/af0584148a6f56d1ce31b8b4d47dc5dd.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/af0584148a6f56d1ce31b8b4d47dc5dd.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>太空军校生们，欢迎你们的到来，让我们大胆地迈向太空军训学院吧！<br><br>双点太空项目的黄金时代已是很久以前了……那时，火箭点亮新闻头条，宇航员几近驰名——堪比鲜有人知的B级片演员。而如今双点县为羽翼未满的太空军训学院打开了大门，双点需要你踏上银河防御的前线，在星系内展开外交，推动太空产业的发展，为双点县做好迎接外星生命的准备。外星人要到了，赶紧假装在干正事。<br><br>我们还在县城轨道中发现了一堆奶酪太空石块。我们需要你建立双点校园首个县外校园，从银河系各个角落招收外星学生，把我们对自身的了解都教给他们。这边的条件可能是差点，不过我们现在可是坐在一座金矿上。<br><br>拂去登月靴上的灰尘，将相位器调到欢乐模式，然后让你的学生们摘星……掏钱吧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/09af1b3ad61281e964e838aadcf86f54.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/09af1b3ad61281e964e838aadcf86f54.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/09af1b3ad61281e964e838aadcf86f54.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>包含內容</strong></h2>：<br>新增 3 处校园地点<br>新增 6 个配有动画特效的课程<br>新增 6 种学生原型<br>新增 3 个活动<br>新增 1 个俱乐部<br>以及海量新物品<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新校园地点</strong></h2><br><strong>宇宙城</strong><br>逐步为郡县对外太空的兴趣重新注入活力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/b90c451aa58ae494569f1ac3001276c4.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/b90c451aa58ae494569f1ac3001276c4.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/b90c451aa58ae494569f1ac3001276c4.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>外星接触</strong><br>管理双点县最新建立的太空军训学院，并准备和外星人接触。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/2cb675ddf94d31a10390384637b8fdd3.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/2cb675ddf94d31a10390384637b8fdd3.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/2cb675ddf94d31a10390384637b8fdd3.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>奶酪堆</strong><br>吸引来自银河各处的学生去巨大太空岩石的表面做研究。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/be17c93d917447482acaa1e871d1f5c0.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/be17c93d917447482acaa1e871d1f5c0.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/be17c93d917447482acaa1e871d1f5c0.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新课程</strong></h2><br>一个不受重力和常识束缚的学科。 <br><strong>宇宙开拓：</strong>利用最新锐的航天技术制造尖点太空车。<br><strong>太空军训学院</strong>：借助这里舒适的环境，逐步提升自己在太空中的自信。<br><strong>太空骑士学校：</strong>传统（地面上的）骑士道的游牧分支 <br><strong>奶酪月球：</strong>没人想看见奶酪的制作过程。<br><strong>学会做人</strong>：外星学生厌倦了道听途说，他们想要未经过滤、新鲜出炉的一手资料。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/86473e9fb7d37d85265e54e61a99cc01.poster.avif?t=1763649247\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/86473e9fb7d37d85265e54e61a99cc01.webm?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884560/extras/86473e9fb7d37d85265e54e61a99cc01.mp4?t=1763649247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>还有：</strong></h2>全新时光旅行俱乐部：时光队长的最新发明，眨眼间就能让充满好奇心的学生享受学校郊游的乐趣。 <br><br><br>全新活动包括科幻大会、太空战斗，以及匪夷所思的外星表演。",
